            "body": "Thanks for the report. There's probably just a tiny wrong decision taken somewhere, e.g. that `__init__.pxd` is not always considered to be a package in all places or so.\r\n\r\nYou tried this with the latest master, right? Could you provide a PR that adds this setup to the existing `tests/run/relative_cimport.srctree` test?",
